findings.title: Sending tokens to dead address instead of really burning (decreasing total supply)
findings.description: Tokens are sent to a dead address rather than being burned, which does not decrease the total supply.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges when they have not renounced ownership, including starting trading, removing limits, changing various settings, and excluding from fees.
